com.cerner.bunsen.mappings

Class Mapping

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cerner.bunsen.mappings.Mapping

  • public class Mapping
extends Object
    A JavaBean to represent a mapping row from one value to another. This class is mutable for easy use as a Spark Dataset<Mapping> instance.
